Send a message to the user. Prefer simple chat-safe formatting in `content`: plain text, blank lines, flat bullets, and short `Label: value` lines. Avoid tables unless the adapter explicitly supports them well. Supports rich cards, interactive elements, polls, optional thread creation, and Slack blocks. Prefer rich formatting for structured or multi-part results (task outcomes, summaries, checklists, comparisons, incident/debug updates, plans): cards/interactions on Discord, blocks on Slack.
